data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 11/18 from 11-3 PM. New HVAC system! Imagine living in a lovingly updated, 2 story home, nestled in the back of a subdivision that's quiet, leafy and peaceful. Well, your home is now available. Upon entry, you'll see how open the interior is with its solid wood floor and bright living space. The updated kitchen and family room will be "the place" for family gatherings and the entire first floor has great flow. The primary suite is down and wait till you see the bathroom!!! The yard with a private entrance backs onto the trails leading to Harberger Park. Amazing! Upstairs you'll find a large, well situated game room, 2 bedrooms a bath and even an office/study nook perfect for work or school. There's even room for another primary suite upstairs if desired! Playhouse in the yard conveys! Come see this one!
